item.title: About
item.dc:creator: rocketinspirit
item.content:encoded:
Rocket, is a storyteller from London. Inspired by the protagonist in the quintessential motion picture Cidade de Deus "City of God". He adopted his name with intentions of embodying Busca pé aka Rocket. Through informal study and exploration he has found strength communicating through photography and writing, in its various forms.

Rocket's work demonstrates his continuous desire to tell stories, evoke emotion and open up dialogue. Rocket has learnt that the medium of art chosen to communicate, influences the potency of a story and how the audience process it. With that stream of consciousness he continues to experiment and adjust his approach in order to convey layered concepts in a simplistic manner.  

Ultimately Rocket's purpose is to be a vessel.

item.title: Work
item.dc:creator: rocketinspirit
item.content:encoded:
"Purity"

Purity is Rocket's life work. Purity showcases Rocket's storytelling in an authentic, visceral and vulnerable manner. As Rocket discovers more about himself and the worlds that orbit him, Purity evolves with him, informing and steering him towards his next experience.

 In essence Purity is a collaboration between Rocket and “La Vida”.
